----------------------------------------------------------

 I. Previous Work:

   Chinese National Standard GB19966-2005
                     provided all 12pt face CJK glyphs between U4E00-U9FA5 and
                     CJK Extension A: U3400-U4DB5
                     http://www.standardcn.com/standard_plan/
                        list_standard_content.asp?stand_id=GB19966-2005

   Unifont Project   Roman Czyborra (roman #czyborra _com)
                     provided 12pt bold face Korean Hangul glyphs
                     http://czyborra.com/unifont/

   Fixed-16x8 pcf font (public domain)

----------------------------------------------------------

